<%# frozen_string_literal: true %>
<% compost_kg = (@stats.kg_diverted * 0.35).round(0).to_i %>
<% co2e_kg    = (@stats.kg_diverted * 1.96).round(0).to_i %>
<% days = (@stats.start_date..@stats.end_date).map(&:day) %>
<% month = @stats.end_date.strftime('%B') %>
♻️ Gooi Weekly Report — <%= @stats.period_label %>

Customers served:  <%= @stats.customers_served %>
Kg collected:      <%= @stats.kg_diverted %> kg
Compost yield:     <%= compost_kg %> kg
CO2e avoided:      <%= co2e_kg %> kg
New customers:     <%= @stats.new_customers %>
Route distance:    <%= @stats.route_kms %> km

---
CANVA TEXT — copy from here:

This week with Gooi
(<%= days.join(', ') %> <%= month %>)

Thanks to <%= @stats.customers_served %> neighbours we kept <%= @stats.kg_diverted %> kg of kitchen scraps out of landfill. That makes about:

• <%= compost_kg %> kg of finished compost for local soil
• <%= co2e_kg %> kg CO₂e emissions avoided
<% if @stats.new_customers.to_i > 0 %>
We also welcomed <%= pluralize(@stats.new_customers, "new household") %> to the Gooi loop — welcome!
<% end %>
Share this and help us grow the numbers!
www.gooi.me
